latestPosts.caption:
I found this awesome place serving delicious momos at super affordable prices (everything under ₹97/- only ). 

Here’s what we tried:

Chicken Kurkure Momos
Chicken Steam Momos
Chicken Smoke Momos
Chicken Cheese Burger
Veg Steam Momos
Chicken Noodles
Veg Fried Rice
French Fries
Blueberry Mojito
Chocolate Oreo Shake
Strawberry Shake

They also have combos starting at just ₹199! For example, you can get 2 Chicken Momo Burgers and 6 pieces of Peri Peri Momos for only ₹199. 😍

📍 Location: Near SGPD Market Complex, Margoa (near Pizza Hut, below SBI ATM).

If you’re a momo lover, do visit this place! Don’t forget to like, follow, and stay tuned for more food finds! ✌️

latestPosts.caption:
Hey guys! I just discovered an amazing hidden spot in Aquem behind Gibson wine shop aquem Margao Goa perfect for school and college hangouts. name @snacks_hunt_ Their ambience is simple yet classy, and the food? Absolutely delicious and pocket-friendly!

Here’s what we tried:
🍔 Veg Cheese Burger
Chicken Cafreal Poi
🌯 Chicken Tandoori Wrap
🍔 Chicken Crispy Burger
🥪 Corn Cheese Sandwich
🍔 Chicken Cafreal Burger
🍽️ Chicken Cafreal Plate
And for drinks:
☕ Cold Coffee
🥝 Kiwi Shake
🍪 Oreo Shake
🥥 Tender Coconut Shake

Everything was flavorful, fresh, and totally worth it! If you’re in Margao, you must give this place a try. 😋
Great for casual meetups, chill scenes, and foodie adventures.

👍 Like this video, follow my page @ankii__1423 for more food finds, and don’t forget to share with your gang

Hey guys! 👋
Today my girls and I visited @hotelcolvakinara  in Colva, and let me tell you — the ambience is wide, classy, and super inviting! ✨

Now let’s talk about the food 🍽️:
We tried their 
tandoori chicken tikka, packed with flavorful spices, along with tandoori gobi and paneer tikka — all absolutely lip-smacking! 😋🔥

For drinks, we went with their refreshing mocktails, which were just perfect to cool down with. 🍹

If you’re in Colva and looking for a spot for your dinner date or a chill evening with friends, this place is definitely worth checking out. 💫

👉 If you like to see more content like this do follow my page @ankii__1423 don’t forget to like this video 

Until next time — bye! 💕
Me, in my own light. 🤎

latestPosts.caption:
I just discovered Shark Tank Verified Cafe @zorko_mapusa_goa , and it’s a MUST-TRY! Their pure veg menu is packed with delicious options like

 Surti coco
Mint and strawberry mojito
 Mac and cheese toast
Peri peri pasta
Veg exotica pizza
Spicy salsa burger with injector

📍 Ground Floor, white castle complex, S. No. S-10,Xim khorlim , Mapusa , Goa 403507

Plus, you can chill with friends and play games! What’s your go-to cafe in Goa? Let me know in the comments! Follow my page @ankii__1423 for more foodie adventures! 😊👍

latestPosts.caption:
@_pizza.burger.point in Mapusa is a hidden gem! With a pocket-friendly menu, it’s perfect for school or college hangouts. Let’s dive into their offerings:

- Juicy burgers
- Delicious pizzas
- Tasty pasta
- Chocolate waffles
- Budget-friendly combos
- Refreshing drinks: coffee, fresh fruit juices, and mojitos

If you’re in Mapusa and looking for a great spot to hang out without breaking the bank, Cafe Pizza Burger Point is a must-visit! If you like to see more content like this do follow by page @ankii__1423 don’t forget to like this video so till than bye
